   21: -module(ct_cth_prio_SUITE).
   22: 
   23: %% Note: This directive should only be used in test suites.
   24: -compile(export_all).
   25: 
   26: -include("ct.hrl").
   27: 
   28: suite() ->
   29:     ([{timetrap, {minutes, 10}},
   30:       {ct_hooks, [{empty_cth,[800],800},
   31: 		  {prio_cth,[1200]},{prio_cth,[1200,1050],1050}]}]).
   32: 
   33: %% Test server callback functions
   34: init_per_suite(Config) ->
   35:     [{ct_hooks, [{empty_cth,[700],700},
   36: 		 {prio_cth,[600,600]},
   37: 		 {prio_cth,[600,200],200}]}|Config].
   38: 
   39: end_per_suite(_Config) ->
   40:     ok.
   41: 
   42: init_per_group(_G, Config) ->
   43:     [{ct_hooks, [{empty_cth,[600],600},
   44: 		 {prio_cth,[900,900]},{prio_cth,[500,900],900}]}|Config].
   45: 
   46: end_per_group(_G, _Config) ->
   47:     ok.
   48: 
   49: init_per_testcase(_TestCase, Config) ->
   50:     Config.
   51: 
   52: end_per_testcase(_TestCase, _Config) ->
   53:     ok.
   54: 
   55: all() ->
   56:     [{group,test_group}].
   57: 
   58: groups() ->
   59:     [{test_group,[],[test_case]}].
   60: 
   61: %% Test cases starts here.
   62: test_case(Config) when is_list(Config) ->
   63:     ok.
